name: ZombielandRules
0:
”Alexa, ask Zombieland Rules what is rule number 3”
”is there a rule about sprinting”
”what's your favorite rule”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: zombieland rules
des: Let Alexa end the arguments about what each of the Zombieland rules are. You can ask about any of the rule numbers and you can also ask based on phrases you recall from the Zombieland rules. You never know, this information could possibly save your life.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
